notes.body:
Description
This is a metabolism model of Mycobacterium tuberculosis H37Rv in SBML format.
iNJ661
The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort. This file has been exported from the software COBRApy and further processed with a JSBML-based in-house application.
This file has been produced by the Systems Biology Research Group and is currently hosted on BiGG knowledgebase and identified by: iNJ661.
